snippet.title: D.O.R.F. Real Time Strategic Conflict - Teaser
snippet.description:
D.O.R.F. Real Time Strategic Conflict is an upcoming indie strategy game inspired by the RTS classics of the 90's and early 2000's.

Play as one of three unique factions, and construct bases, harvest resources and assemble giant armies to dominate your enemies.

Website: https://www.dorf-rts.com/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/DorfRTS
Support us on Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/dorfRTS
Trailer music by Mister Kad: https://misterkad.bandcamp.com/


#rts #pcgaming #realtimestrategygames #gaming
